'''[[密歇根州|密歇根州]]州旗'''为一面深蓝色旗帜，中心为州徽，州旗图案由密歇根州法令规定。<ref name="MCL 209">[http://www.legislature.mi.gov/(S(xsplfn311t0tbe45nqbnaibg))/mileg.aspx?page=getObject&objectName=mcl-Act-209-of-1911 Act 209 of 1911 Coat-of-Arms and State Flag] {{Wayback|url=http://www.legislature.mi.gov/(S(xsplfn311t0tbe45nqbnaibg))/mileg.aspx?page=getObject&objectName=mcl-Act-209-of-1911 |date=20171016221904 }} in Michigan Compiled Laws</ref>

==设计==
州旗上的州徽中有一个浅蓝色盾牌，描绘了太阳在湖泊和[[半岛|半岛]]间升起的画面，一个人举起一只手，另一手持有一个长[[枪|枪]]，象征[[和平|和平]]和保卫他的权利的能力。扶盾者为[[加拿大马鹿|加拿大马鹿]]和[[驼鹿|驼鹿]]，这一扶盾者来自[[哈德逊湾公司|哈德逊湾公司]]的纹章，[[白頭海鵰|白头鹰]]则象征[[美国|美国]]。<ref name=netstate>{{Cite web |url=http://www.netstate.com/states/symb/flags/mi_flag.htm |title=www.netstate.com |accessdate=2013-04-29 |archive-date=2013-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130510105704/http://www.netstate.com/states/symb/flags/mi_flag.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>

